	Description = {
		"@eng:Normalizes the input <c>Vector</c> and outputs the resulting unit-vector.\\n\\nUnlike the builtin <c>normalize</c> node, this node checks for null vectors.\\nThis prevents normalizing a null vector and getting an Infinity or NaN vector in return.\\nWorks on any vector dimensions.\\n\\nHigher precision than <c>safe normalize fast</c>, but slower to compute.",
	};
