		"@eng:This node tracks the time elapsed since a condition was <c>true</c>\\n\\nIt features classic \"stopwatch timer\" controls: <c>Start</c>, <c>Pause</c>, <c>Stop</c>, <c>Restart</c> and <c>Reset</c>.\\nIt can be auto-started when the particle is born using the <c>Autostart</c> input.\\n\\nIt outputs the tracked time, as well as whether or not the timer is currently running.",
