	GraphUsage = EventGraph;
	Description = {
		"@eng:This node routes the input events to one of its two output pins based on the result of a build-version test.\\n\\nThis test is compile time, so there is no additional cost for this at runtime.\\nIt allows to activate different parts of the effect based on, for example, the platform the effect is baked for.\\nYou can also setup your own build versions & tags in the project settings to bake effects for different quality settings, or any other custom criteria.",
